§ COHERENCE-ENGINE (Artifact Ascension)
§§ source : DEPRECATED/GDDs/ARTIFACT_ASCENSION_SPEC.md
§§ status @ ✓ design-complete · ‼ deterministic ¬ random
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : every-great-loot-system-needs-recognition-of-coherence
§ anti-Diablo-Primal-Ancients : ¬ lottery · ✓ recognition-of-craftsmanship

§ 13-axes-of-item-composition :
  1 Form              ← ItemDefinition table
  2 Components[]      ← ItemAssembly hot-swappable
  3 Material          ← MaterialDefinition per-component
  4 ComponentRarity   ← Common → Legendary per-component
  5 Affixes           ← rolled per-component ⊗ interaction-rules
  6 CulturalDoctrine  ← CombatDoctrine.from generating-faction
  7 Quality           ← CraftingSystem formula-output
  8 LatticeSockets[]  ← Modular Spell Cartridges
  9 Resonance         ← per-element attunement.from use
 10 Patina            ← Biography-driven passive-effects
 11 Corruption-Blessing ← spectrum [-1.0, +1.0]
 12 Cross-Genre-Compat ← genre-bridging + compat-penalty
 13 CoherenceScore    ← capstone evaluating axes 1-12

§ 6-Harmony-Dimensions : ElementalPurity ⊕ MaterialHarmony ⊕ CulturalCoherence ⊕ AffixSynergyDepth ⊕ BiographyWeight ⊕ ParadoxTension
§ tie-break-priority : Paradox > Affix > Elemental > Cultural > Biography > Material (rarer-dominances-priority)

§ Ascension :
  ‼ deterministic : same-state → same-score → same-Epithet · t∞
  ‼ rewards-intent ¬ luck : random-loot rarely-Ascends · deliberate-buildcraft reliably-does
  ◐ compelling ¬ mandatory : un-Ascended-with-good-components still-top-tier · gap = ~15-25% power + unique-mechanic
  ✓ personal : Retroactive-Substrate-regenerates-per-run + Biography-accumulates → most-Ascended-items unique-to-builder

§ AscensionTrigger ∈ {Crafting · ComponentSwap · AuraApplication · CartridgeSocket · ResonanceGrowth · PatinaAccrual · CorruptionShift · TransmuterModified · PreAscended}

§ Item-Biography ring-buffer :
  ⊑ MaxEntries = 64 · TotalEventsWitnessed = lifetime-counter
  ⊑ aggregated-counters : ElementalKills · ElementalBlocks · CreatureTypeKills · FactionKills · BiomesTraversed · NearDeathSurvivals · NemesisKills · NemesisDeaths · RunsSurvived · OwnersCount
  ⊑ BiographyEventType : Kill · NemesisKill · NemesisDeath · NemesisRecovered · NearDeathSurvival · MassKill · BossKill · BiomeFirstEntry · HazardSurvival · ExtremeTempExposure · GenreCrossing · FactionMemberKill · DeityOfferingPresent · TradeHandoff

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 : NEW crate `cssl-host-coherence-engine` (POD-2-extension @ wave-7+) · 13-axis evaluator + Epithet generator · 6 Harmony rankers · BTreeMap-deterministic serde · ≥ 30 tests

