§ NEXUS-BAZAAR (Multiversal Auction House)
§§ source : DEPRECATED/GDDs/NEXUS_BAZAAR_SPEC.md
§§ status @ ✓ design-complete · ‼ "sells-history ¬ stats"
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : 13-axis-variation makes-perfect-meaningless · Bazaar = gallery-of-singular-artifacts ¬ commodity-exchange

§ access-gating @ NG+ Stabilization :
  ⊑ MinCompletedRuns = 10
  ⊑ MinLabyrinthDepth = 50
  ⊑ MinAscendedItemsCrafted = 3
  ⊑ MinFormsbookEntries = 40
  ⊑ MinDistinctGenresExplored = 3
  ⊑ MinFactionReputations = 2 @ Friendly (>600)
  ⊑ MinDeityFavor = 1 (positive)

§ 5-tier-license :
  T0 Visitor    ← NG+ unlock · browse-only
  T1 Patron     ← 1 NG+ run completed · buy-only
  T2 Merchant   ← 2 Ascended in NG+ · 1 active listing
  T3 Artisan    ← 5 Ascended @ Coherence ≥ 80 · 3 active · badge
  T4 Grandmaster ← 1 Ascended @ Coherence ≥ 90 ⊗ 10+ sold · 5 active · premium-stall · Commissions

§ currency = Stabilized-Essence (SE)
  ‼ NEVER-purchasable-with-real-money · t∞
  ‼ generated-through-NG+-play-only

§ SE-earn-sources : NG+ run extract (50-200) · depth-milestones (25/each) · Ascending (30) · first-Epithet-category (100) · Nemesis-kill (40) · Deconstruct-Ascended (15-50) · Commission (100-500)

§ SE-sinks : listing-fee 10% · transaction-tax 5% · stall-upgrades (50-500 cosmetic) · vault-rental (10/slot/cycle) · commission-fee 20% · Multiversal-Nemesis-bounties · Nexus-Breach-room-unlock (200/type)

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 : Bazaar = `cssl-edge` route + `cssl-supabase` migrations 0021-0025 (bazaar_listings · bazaar_transactions · bazaar_commissions · stabilized_essence_balances · multiversal_nemesis_bounties) + `cssl-host-bazaar` Rust crate (offline-snapshot + price-suggest)

