§ OUROBOROID-COSMOLOGY (Lore Bible · 6 Rings)
§§ source : DEPRECATED/GDDs/OUROBOROID_COSMOLOGY.md
§§ status @ ✓ lore-bible-complete · ‼ ¬ exposition-dump · embed-everywhere
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : "The Labyrinth is what the process looks like from the inside"
§ ¬ map · ¬ timeline · ¬ creation-myth · ✓ cosmological-engine

§ 6-Rings @ player-comprehension-gradient :
  R1 What-Player-Sees      ← roguelike · infinite · procedural · materially-consistent · "complete-and-satisfying-in-itself"
  R2 What-Player-Suspects  ← Architectural-Metabolism · Entity-Rhyming · Lore-Echoes · "illegible-until-context"
  R3 What-Player-Knows     ← Ouroboroid = Hydra-of-self-consuming-concepts · ¬ namable · Russell's-Paradox-ontological
  R4 What-Player-Feels     ← "You have no power over me and/or us" = thesis-stance ¬ victory-condition
  R5 How-It-Manifests      ← procgen=new-heads · room-transform=digestion · materials=concepts-mid-metabolism · enemies=immune-response · Ascension=persistence-across-cycle
  R6 What-Scholars-Tried   ← Dwarven-Axiomatists · partial-proofs · self-reference-failure-points

§ lore-delivery-comprehension-gradient :
  Ambient   ← always-visible · ¬ literacy-required · room/material/entity-names suggest-organic-processes
  Textual   ← visible-to-readers · flavor-text · wall-inscriptions · NPC-dialogue · book-fragments
  Structural ← visible-to-systems-thinkers · same-algorithms-across-entities · room-patterns-mirror-digestion
  Meta      ← visible-to-deeply-literate · roguelike-structure-IS-cosmology · player-behavior-enacts-cycle

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 : `cssl-host-narrative-engine` Rust crate (storylet-sieve + Propp's-functions + comprehension-gradient classifier) · 6-ring tagging applied to ALL flavor-text · POD-3 .csl game-logic embeds via narrative-engine FFI

