§ FLUX-DYNAMICS (Magic ↔ Science Unified)
§§ source : DEPRECATED/GDDs/CHEMISTRY_MAGIC_CRAFTING_BIBLE.md
§§ status @ ✓ design-complete · ‼ one-simulation-two-vocabularies
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : "magic is chemistry the player doesn't understand yet · chemistry is magic the player has mastered"

§ 2-domain-architecture :
  Material-Domain ← Physics · Chemistry · Thermodynamics · Currency=Temp/Pressure/ChemicalPotential · Observable-by-everyone
  Aetheric-Domain ← Spell-Lattice topology · Node-rules · Currency=Aura/Resonance/Attunement · Observable-by-magical-perception

§ TRANSDUCER-LAYER (bridge) :
  Sensor-Signals    ← Material → Aetheric (lava-tile@1200°C → Fire-energy → spell-Source-node taps free)
  Actuator-Signals  ← Aetheric → Material (Release-node "Fire intensity 0.8" → +400°C @ target-tile → chemistry)

§ 15-material-properties : Density · MeltingPoint · BoilingPoint · Hardness · Conductivity · Flammability · AcidResistance · FatigueRate · Reactivity · Toxicity · MagicAffinity · Opacity · Elasticity · Solubility · Volatility

§ material-categories : Metals · Stone · Organic · Fluid · Gas · Exotic · Alloys (Bronze=Cu+Sn · Steel=Fe+C · Electrum=Au+Ag · Orichalcum=Cu+Aethite · Nullsteel=Fe+Voidite)

§ port-target-for-LoA-v13 : `cssl-host-flux-dynamics` Rust crate · Material/Aetheric tick-simulator · Transducer-event bus · 15-property MaterialDB · `cssl-host-spell-lattice` Rust crate (already-planned in W7 POD-2 as `cssl-host-spell-graph`) extends with TransducerSignals

