§ LIVING-MULTIVERSE (NEW · Apocky 2026-05-01 directive)
§§ extends Nexus-Bazaar from "shared-marketplace" → "shared-evolving-multiversal-layer"
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : multiverse = aggregate-player-behavior shapes-the-shared-substrate
  ⊑ player-A's-defeated-Nemesis becomes player-B's-rumor (cross-shard)
  ⊑ player-cohort's collective-cocreative-bias drifts the multiverse-aesthetic per-region
  ⊑ Ouroboroid-cosmology naturally-supports this : aggregate-defiance becomes-new-head

§ implementation-anchors :
  ⊑ `cssl-host-multiplayer-signaling` (W4 ✓ landed) — peer-room state-machine
  ⊑ `cssl-host-mp-transport` + `cssl-host-mp-transport-real` (W5c + W7) — WebSocket / Supabase-relay
  ⊑ `cssl-supabase` 0010-0013 (game-state-snapshots · session-index · sovereign-cap-audit)
  ⊑ `cssl-supabase` 0007-0009 (cocreative-bias-vectors cross-session)
  ⊑ NEW `cssl-supabase` migration `0021_living_multiverse.sql` : multiverse_aggregate_state · regional_aesthetic_drift · cross-player-rumors · nemesis-cross-shard-propagation

§ guarantees :
  ‼ player-sovereignty preserved : opt-out-of-multiverse-influence = unilateral
  ‼ no-PvP-griefing : player-A actions affect player-B only via OPT-IN rumor/aesthetic-drift channels
  ‼ all cross-player-influence audit-emits via cssl-host-attestation
  ‼ shared-state ¬ replaces single-player-canonical-truth · is-a-LAYER-OVER

