§ MONETIZATION (NEW · Apocky 2026-05-01 directive · ¬ pay-for-power)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ AXIOM @ ¬ negotiable · t∞ :
  N! pay-for-power · N! pay-for-gear-stats · N! pay-to-skip-Coherence · N! Stabilized-Essence-purchasable
  ✓ pay-for-cosmetics · ✓ pay-for-cadence-tier-skips · ✓ pay-for-content-expansions

§ BATTLE-PASS (seasonal · 90-day cycles)
  ⊑ free-track : ALL gameplay-relevant unlocks (room-types · base-cosmetics · seasonal-storylets) at slower-cadence
  ⊑ premium-track : faster-cadence · exclusive-cosmetics · early-access-room-types (cosmetics-only · gameplay-symmetric)
  ⊑ tier-skip : Stripe-payment · cosmetic-channel-only
  ⊑ premium-currency = "Aetheric-Shards" · Stripe-purchasable · spent on battle-pass-tiers + gacha-pulls + cosmetic-direct-purchase
  ⊑ ¬ Aetheric-Shards purchase Stabilized-Essence · ¬ Aetheric-Shards purchase gear · ¬ Aetheric-Shards purchase any-Coherence-axis-influence

§ GACHA (cosmetics-only · ethical)
  ⊑ pulls-yield : visual-themes · weapon-skins · companion-cosmetics · stall-decorations · emotes · UI-themes
  ⊑ ¬ pulls-yield : gear · stats · power · Coherence-bias · room-types-gameplay-relevant · class-unlocks
  ⊑ pity-system : guaranteed-rare every-N-pulls · transparent-rates published per-jurisdiction-laws
  ⊑ duplicates : auto-convert to "Aetheric-Dust" → trade for currently-equipped-cosmetic-variants
  ⊑ NEVER : loot-box-with-power-rewards · per-jurisdiction-compliance (UK · BE · NL · DE · etc.)

§ STRIPE-INTEGRATION
  ⊑ payment-processor for Aetheric-Shards purchase
  ⊑ NEW `cssl-edge` routes : `/api/payments/stripe/checkout` · `/api/payments/stripe/webhook` · `/api/payments/stripe/refund-request`
  ⊑ Server-side webhook signature-verification · idempotency-keys · audit-emit per-transaction
  ⊑ NEW `cssl-supabase` migration `0022_payments.sql` : stripe_customers · stripe_payment_intents · aetheric_shard_balances · cosmetic_purchases · gacha_pulls · battle_pass_tiers
  ⊑ ¬ store : raw-card-numbers · CVV · full-PAN · ALL via Stripe-tokenization (PCI-DSS-SAQ-A scope-min)
  ⊑ refunds : within 14-days no-questions-asked · jurisdiction-mandated-rights respected
  ⊑ player-sovereignty : full-account-data-export + delete-on-request (GDPR · CCPA · etc.)

§ ATTESTATION-INVARIANT @ monetization :
  ‼ every-Stripe-transaction emits `payment.charge` audit-event with $amount · cosmetic-only-flag · stripe-payment-intent-id
  ‼ every-gacha-pull emits `gacha.pull` audit-event with rarity · drop-rate-snapshot · pity-counter-state
  ‼ every-battle-pass-tier-unlock emits `battlepass.tier` audit-event
  ‼ NEW `cssl-host-attestation` directive-axis : "EconomicTransparency" tracks all-monetization-events for player-self-audit
  ‼ player-self-audit-dashboard @ `cssl-edge`/transparency/spending visualizes all-transactions + total-spent + refund-history

